00:18:59.790 --> 00:19:06.000
OK, so that's this part of
the Schrodinger equation.

00:19:06.000 --> 00:19:08.560
I want to remind you of
another concept called

00:19:08.560 --> 00:19:10.890
the current--
probability current.

00:19:13.890 --> 00:19:17.980
Probability current.

00:19:17.980 --> 00:19:18.840
What is it?

00:19:18.840 --> 00:19:22.420
It's a j of x and
t-- that you will

00:19:22.420 --> 00:19:26.570
