00:21:08.750 --> 00:21:10.960
Think about it.

00:21:10.960 --> 00:21:14.990
This means charge conservation
as we usually understand,

00:21:14.990 --> 00:21:18.610
and the way to do it--
I'm saying just in words--

00:21:18.610 --> 00:21:20.700
is you think of
a volume, you can

00:21:20.700 --> 00:21:23.450
see how much charge
is inside, and you

00:21:23.450 --> 00:21:26.070
see that the rate of
change of the charge

00:21:26.070 --> 00:21:30.750
is proportional to the current
that is escaping the volume.

00:21:30.750 --> 00:21:34.680
Which is to say, charge is
never destroyed or created.

00:21:34.680 --> 00:21:37.720
It can escape a volume,
because the charges are moving,

00:21:37.720 --> 00:21:41.140
but if it doesn't escape, well,
the charge remains the same.

00:21:41.140 --> 00:21:42.920
So, this is charge conservation.

00:21:42.920 --> 00:21:45.150
And this is the same thing.

00:21:45.150 --> 00:21:47.720
So the divergence
of j in this case

00:21:47.720 --> 00:21:55.740
reduces to dj dx plus
d Rho dt equals zero.

00:22:00.530 --> 00:22:03.250
It has a very similar
interpretation.

00:22:03.250 --> 00:22:06.500
So, perhaps in
equations, it's easier

00:22:06.500 --> 00:22:09.290
to think of interpretation.

00:22:09.290 --> 00:22:14.250
Consider the real line
and the point a and b,

00:22:14.250 --> 00:22:16.550
with a less than b.

00:22:16.550 --> 00:22:21.190
And define the
probability pab of t

00:22:21.190 --> 00:22:31.940
