00:23:38.740 --> 00:23:41.210
So, what does that mean?

00:23:41.210 --> 00:23:43.730
You can have the particle
here at any time.

00:23:43.730 --> 00:23:46.900
But if you want to know how
the probability changing,

00:23:46.900 --> 00:23:50.010
you must see how
