00:23:50.010 --> 00:23:51.570
or how it's leaking from b.

00:23:51.570 --> 00:23:54.740
Now j's are defined,
by convention,

00:23:54.740 --> 00:23:56.310
positive to the right.

00:23:56.310 --> 00:23:59.620
So, if there's a current--
